@startuml PMA_DFD_Level0
' Personalized Medical Assistant - Data Flow Diagram (Level 0 / Context Diagram)
' Generated: November 7, 2025
' To use in draw.io: Arrange → Insert → Advanced → PlantUML

title Personalized Medical Assistant\nData Flow Diagram - Level 0 (Context Diagram)

' Professional colorful styling
skinparam backgroundColor #F8F9FA

skinparam rectangle {
    BorderColor #424242
    BorderThickness 3
    FontSize 14
    FontStyle bold
}

skinparam actor {
    BorderColor #424242
    BorderThickness 2
    FontSize 13
    FontStyle bold
}

skinparam database {
    BorderColor #424242
    BorderThickness 2
    FontSize 12
    FontStyle bold
}

skinparam arrow {
    Color #424242
    Thickness 2
    FontSize 11
    FontColor #212121
}

skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #E8F5E9
    BorderColor #2E7D32
    BorderThickness 2
    FontSize 11
}

' ============ Layout ============
left to right direction

' ============ External Entities ============
actor Patient #90CAF9
actor Doctor #66BB6A

' ============ Central System ============
rectangle "PMA System" as PMA #A5D6A7

' ============ Data Stores ============
database "D1: Patient Data" as D1 #FFB74D
database "D2: Doctor Data" as D2 #FFB74D
database "D3: ML Models" as D3 #CE93D8

' ============ Patient to System ============
Patient --> PMA : Patient Data\n(Login, Records, Symptoms)

' ============ System to Patient ============
PMA --> Patient : Results & Notifications\n(Predictions, Appointments, Reminders)

' ============ Doctor to System ============
Doctor --> PMA : Doctor Input\n(Login, Notes, Prescriptions)

' ============ System to Doctor ============
PMA --> Doctor : Patient Information\n(History, Notifications)

' ============ System to Data Stores ============
PMA --> D1 : Read/Write
PMA --> D2 : Read/Write
PMA --> D3 : Read/Write

' ============ Notes ============
note right of PMA
**Core Functions:**
• Authentication
• Medical Records
• ML Prediction
• Appointments
• Communication
• Reminders
end note

@enduml
